            "20. Open `desktop-next-step.md` or parse `desktop-next-step.json` when you want a generated read-only decision report; run `desktop_next_step` from `commands.json` when project files or local config changed after pack generation.",
            "21. Open `project-status.md` or parse `project-status.json` before writing, then open `continuity-audit.md` or parse `continuity-audit.json`; handle `must_fix` and `review` actions first.",
