        "| First time using this pack | `quick-install.md` then `install-local.md` | `bash install-local.sh`, `powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\install-local.ps1`, `install-local.cmd`, or double-click `install-local.command`; apply only after review | Local skill, MCP config, project init, and local checks when allowed |",
        "| You only need to refresh an older local install | `upgrade-local.md` | `bash upgrade-local.sh`, `powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\upgrade-local.ps1`, `upgrade-local.cmd`, or double-click `upgrade-local.command`; apply only after review | Installed skill and selected MCP entry refreshed; project state stays |",
        "| You want to remove the local MCP entry | `uninstall-local.md` | `bash uninstall-local.sh`, `powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\\uninstall-local.ps1`, `uninstall-local.cmd`, or double-click `uninstall-local.command`; apply only after review | Installed skill and selected MCP entry removed; project state stays |",
