        "| You want to check whether this pack is usable on the current machine | `pack-doctor.md` and `pack-doctor.json` | `pack_doctor` or `pack_doctor_json` in `commands.json` or `commands.txt` | Checks metadata, commands, referenced Kit paths, key files, script permissions, and local interpreter availability without writing project state |",
