        "| You want the kit to choose the next command from current state | `desktop-next-step.md`, `desktop-next-step.json`, `project-status.json`, `client-compatibility.json`, and `commands.json` | `desktop_next_step` in `commands.json` or `commands.txt` when files changed after pack generation | Read-only report names the primary action, related file, command, and write boundaries |",
