        "| A desktop agent finished a meaningful step | `agent-start.md` and `commands.json` | `record_agent_activity` in `commands.json` or `commands.txt` after review | The next agent sees a short activity or handoff summary without reading chat history |",
        f"| You need real desktop client proof | `{DESKTOP_EVIDENCE_SESSION_MD_FILE}`, `{DESKTOP_EVIDENCE_SESSION_JSON_FILE}`, `{DESKTOP_EVIDENCE_RUNBOOK_MD_FILE}`, `{DESKTOP_EVIDENCE_RUNBOOK_JSON_FILE}`, `real-client-walkthrough.md`, `client-prompts.md`, and `checklist.md` | Follow prompts inside the desktop app | Real client evidence is ready to paste |",
        f"| You copied evidence text | `{DESKTOP_EVIDENCE_REVIEW_HTML_FILE}`, `{DESKTOP_EVIDENCE_REVIEW_MD_FILE}`, `{DESKTOP_EVIDENCE_REVIEW_JSON_FILE}`, `{DESKTOP_EVIDENCE_GAPS_MD_FILE}`, `{DESKTOP_EVIDENCE_GAPS_JSON_FILE}`, `evidence-to-results.md`, and `desktop-evidence.txt` | `desktop_evidence_packet`, `desktop_evidence_review`, `desktop_evidence_gaps`, then `ingest_evidence` in `commands.json` or `commands.txt` | Evidence status, missing checks, per-check evidence gaps, saved records, and safety warnings are visible before an imported results draft is created |",
